    "slug": "know-that-god-loves-you-very-very-much-and-remind-others-that-they-are-loved-t",
    "texto": "Know that God loves you very, very much. And remind others that they are loved too. If they don’t want to hear that God loves them, then tell them you love them. It will be just as important! Beliefs vary, but love always works!",
